<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śōbhanamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sa jayati narapālō ratnasiṁhāsanastō vijeyanagaravāsī kīrtipū
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rtyā vilāsī nruganaḷanahusyādīnmōca(ṁ)ya(ṁ)n rājanītyā nirupamabhujavī
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ryyaudāryyabhūra(cyutākhyāṁśrī A)cutēṁdraḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="4"/>dānapālaneyōrmadhyē dānātsrēyōnupālanaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dānāsvargamavāpnōti pālanādacyutaṁ padaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svadattādviguṇaṁ pu(ṁ)ṇyaṁ paradattānu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>pālanaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> paradattāpahārēṇa svadattaṁ niṣphalaṁ bhavēt <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasuṁdharā<unclear>ṁ</unclear> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ṣaṣṭirvaruṣasahasrāṇi
<lb n="6"/>viṣṭhāyāṁ jyāyatē krimi<unclear>ḥ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yēkayiva bhaginī lōkē sarvēśāmēva bhūbhujāṁ na bhōjyāna karagrāhya dēvadattā vasuṁdharā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="7"/>sāmā(ṁ)nyōyaṁ dharmasētuṁ nrupāṇāṁ kālē kālē pālanīyō bhavadbhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> sarvānētē bhāvinaḥ pārṭhivēṁdrā(ṁ)n bhūyō
<lb n="8"/>bhūyō yācatē rāmacaṁdraḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

